{"content":"<header class=\"shadow-md sm:p-2 w-full bg-white dark:text-white dark:bg-navy mb-20\" data-hk=\"3.0\"><div data-hk=\"3.1\" class=\"flex justify-between\"><a href=\"en-US/\" class=\"justify-self-start self-center m-3 ml-5 text-md sm:text-2xl\" data-hk=\"3.2\">Perseus</a><div data-hk=\"3.3\" class=\"xs:hidden m-3 mr-5 tham tham-e-spin tham-w-6 \"><div class=\"tham-box\" data-hk=\"3.4\"><div data-hk=\"3.5\" class=\"dark:bg-white tham-inner\"></div></div></div><nav class=\"hidden xs:flex\" data-hk=\"3.6\"><ul data-hk=\"3.7\" class=\"mr-5 flex\"><li data-hk=\"4.0\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a class=\"px-2\" data-hk=\"4.1\" href=\"en-US/docs\">Docs</a></li><li data-hk=\"4.2\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a href=\"en-US/comparisons\" class=\"px-2\" data-hk=\"4.3\">Comparisons</a></li><li data-hk=\"4.4\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a data-hk=\"4.5\" class=\"px-2\" href=\"en-US/plugins\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></div><nav class=\"xs:hidden w-full text-center justify-center hidden\" data-hk=\"3.8\" id=\"mobile_nav_menu\"><ul class=\"mr-5\" data-hk=\"3.9\"><li data-hk=\"5.0\" class=\"m-3 p-1\"><a class=\"px-2\" href=\"en-US/docs\" data-hk=\"5.1\">Docs</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\" data-hk=\"5.2\"><a href=\"en-US/comparisons\" data-hk=\"5.3\" class=\"px-2\">Comparisons</a></li><li class=\"m-3 p-1\" data-hk=\"5.4\"><a class=\"px-2\" data-hk=\"5.5\" href=\"en-US/plugins\">Plugins</a></li></ul></nav></header><div data-hk=\"3.10\" class=\"overflow-y-scroll\"><main data-hk=\"3.11\" class=\"h-full\"><div class=\"bg-cover h-full flex justify-center items-center text-center dark:text-white\" data-hk=\"2.0\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/splash_page_bg.svg&quot;), url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/polygon_scatter.svg&quot;);\"><div data-hk=\"2.1\"><p data-hk=\"2.2\" class=\"text-7xl xs:text-8xl sm:text-9xl p-2 font-extrabold\">Perseus</p><p class=\"text-lg\" data-hk=\"2.3\">The Rust framework for the modern web.</p><br data-hk=\"2.4\"/><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center\" data-hk=\"2.5\"><a data-hk=\"2.6\" href=\"en-US/docs\" class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\">Get Started</a><a data-hk=\"2.7\" class=\"inline-flex items-center py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl dark:text-white ring-4 ring-indigo-500 hover:ring-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus\"><span data-hk=\"2.8\" class=\"mr-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 17 16\" fill=\"none\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\"><g clip-path=\"url(githublogo)\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M8.18391.249268C3.82241.249268.253906 3.81777.253906 8.17927c0 3.46933 2.279874 6.44313 5.451874 7.53353.3965.0991.49563-.1983.49563-.3965v-1.3878c-2.18075.4956-2.67638-.9912-2.67638-.9912-.3965-.8922-.89212-1.1895-.89212-1.1895-.69388-.4957.09912-.4957.09912-.4957.793.0992 1.1895.793 1.1895.793.69388 1.2887 1.88338.8922 2.27988.6939.09912-.4956.29737-.8921.49562-1.0904-1.78425-.1982-3.5685-.8921-3.5685-3.96496 0-.89212.29738-1.586.793-2.08162-.09912-.19825-.3965-.99125.09913-2.08163 0 0 .69387-.19825 2.18075.793.59475-.19825 1.28862-.29737 1.9825-.29737.69387 0 1.38775.09912 1.98249.29737 1.4869-.99125 2.1808-.793 2.1808-.793.3965 1.09038.1982 1.88338.0991 2.08163.4956.59475.793 1.28862.793 2.08162 0 3.07286-1.8834 3.66766-3.66764 3.86586.29737.3965.59474.8921.59474 1.586v2.1808c0 .1982.0991.4956.5948.3965 3.172-1.0904 5.4518-4.0642 5.4518-7.53353-.0991-4.3615-3.6676-7.930002-8.02909-7.930002z\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"></path></g><defs class=\"jsx-120409797\"><clipPath id=\"githublogo\" class=\"jsx-120409797\"><path fill=\"transparent\" d=\"M0 0h15.86v15.86H0z\" transform=\"translate(.253906 .0493164)\"></path></clipPath></defs></svg></span><span data-hk=\"2.9\"> GitHub</span></a></div></div></div><div data-hk=\"2.10\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/stacked_waves.svg&quot;);\" class=\"bg-cover py-4 text-white\"><div data-hk=\"2.11\" class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full\"><p data-hk=\"2.12\" class=\"p-1 xs:p-4 max-w-7xl\">Perseus is a web development framework built entirely in Rust, designed to empower efficient development of the next generation of lightning-fast sites for the modern web. It comes with server-side rendering, static site generation, internationalization, and inferred routing built-in, letting you build even the most complex sites in a breeze.</p></div><br data-hk=\"2.13\"/><div class=\"flex justify-center\" data-hk=\"2.14\"><ul class=\"text-center max-w-7xl mx-2\" data-hk=\"2.15\"><li data-hk=\"2.16\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\" data-hk=\"2.17\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\" data-hk=\"2.18\">Static generation</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\" data-hk=\"2.19\">Pre-render pages at build-time before you've even had any visits!</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\" data-hk=\"2.20\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\" data-hk=\"2.21\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\" data-hk=\"2.22\">Server-side rendering</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\" data-hk=\"2.23\">Render pages on the server to reduce the load on the client.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"2.24\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\" data-hk=\"2.25\"><p data-hk=\"2.26\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Internationalization</p><p data-hk=\"2.27\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Out-of-the-box support for building your app in multiple languages.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\" data-hk=\"2.28\"><div data-hk=\"2.29\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\" data-hk=\"2.30\">Incremental generation</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\" data-hk=\"2.31\">Render pages on-demand and cache them for future use.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"2.32\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"2.33\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"2.34\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Revalidation</p><p data-hk=\"2.35\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Rebuild pages automatically without lifting a finger.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"2.36\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"2.37\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"2.38\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">CLI</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\" data-hk=\"2.39\">Comes with a friendly interface to accelerate your development pace.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"2.40\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"2.41\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"2.42\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Inferred routing</p><p class=\"text-gray-100\" data-hk=\"2.43\">You do your app, Perseus does the rest automatically.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\" data-hk=\"2.44\"><div data-hk=\"2.45\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p data-hk=\"2.46\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">App shell</p><p data-hk=\"2.47\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Get all the benefits of a single-page app without any of the downsides.</p></div></li><li class=\"inline-block align-top\" data-hk=\"2.48\"><div class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\" data-hk=\"2.49\"><p data-hk=\"2.50\" class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\">Single-command deployment</p><p data-hk=\"2.51\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Take your apps to production with one command.</p></div></li><li data-hk=\"2.52\" class=\"inline-block align-top\"><div data-hk=\"2.53\" class=\"text-left cursor-pointer rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-100 p-8 max-w-sm\"><p class=\"text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl\" data-hk=\"2.54\">Static exporting</p><p data-hk=\"2.55\" class=\"text-gray-100\">Deploy your apps without needing a server.</p></div></li></ul></div><br data-hk=\"2.56\"/><br data-hk=\"2.57\"/><div data-hk=\"2.58\" class=\"flex justify-center text-center text-lg w-full p-1 xs:p-4\"><div class=\"p-4 shadow-2xl rounded-xl max-w-lg\" data-hk=\"2.59\"><p class=\"underline text-2xl mb-2\" data-hk=\"2.60\">Building a Perseus App:</p><ol class=\"list-decimal list-inside\" data-hk=\"2.61\"><li data-hk=\"2.62\"><span data-hk=\"2.63\"><!--#-->Install Perseus:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"2.64\">cargo install perseus-cli</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"2.65\"><span data-hk=\"2.66\">Build your awesome app with <a href=\"https://github.com/sycamore-rs/sycamore\" class=\"underline\">Sycamore</a></span></li><li data-hk=\"2.67\"><span data-hk=\"2.68\"><!--#-->Serve your app locally:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"2.69\">perseus serve</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"2.70\"><span data-hk=\"2.71\"><!--#-->Deploy your app to a single directory:<!--/--> <code data-hk=\"2.72\">perseus deploy</code></span></li><li data-hk=\"2.73\"><span data-hk=\"2.74\">Upload that to a server!</span></li></ol></div></div></div><div style=\"background: url(&quot;.perseus/static/svg/cta_bg.svg&quot;);background-size:cover;\" data-hk=\"2.75\" class=\"pb-24 flex flex-col justify-center text-white\"><div data-hk=\"2.76\" class=\"text-3xl 2xs:text-4xl xs:text-5xl sm:text-6xl p-2 font-extrabold text-center\"><p data-hk=\"2.77\">What are you waiting for?</p><p data-hk=\"2.78\">Dive in and start building for the web of tomorrow!</p></div><br data-hk=\"2.79\"/><div data-hk=\"2.80\" class=\"flex justify-center\"><a class=\"py-3 px-4 m-2 text-xl font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 transition-colors duration-200\" href=\"en-US/docs\" data-hk=\"2.81\">Get Started</a></div><br data-hk=\"2.82\"/><div data-hk=\"2.83\" class=\"flex justify-center\"><a href=\"en-US/comparisons\" data-hk=\"2.84\" class=\"py-2 px-4 m-2 font-semibold rounded-lg shadow-2xl text-white bg-indigo-500 hover:bg-indigo-400 transition-colors duration-200\">Or See How Perseus Compares</a></div></div></main></div><footer class=\"w-full flex justify-center py-5 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-navy-deep\" data-hk=\"3.12\"><p class=\"dark:text-white mx-5 text-center\" data-hk=\"3.13\"><span data-hk=\"3.14\">© <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7\" class=\"underline\">arctic-hen7</a> ⁨2021⁩, see license <a href=\"https://github.com/arctic-hen7/perseus/blob/main/LICENSE\" class=\"underline\">here</a>.</span></p></footer>","state":null,"head":"<title data-hk=\"1.0\">Perseus</title>"}